            . I am a <rs id="t18210606-32-viclabel187" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-32-victim372 t18210606-32-viclabel187"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18210606-32-crimeloc188">Upper Thames-street</placeName>
